    "---\n",
    "## Part 2 — Selecting Specific Columns\n",
    "\n",
    "Rather than using `*`, you can name the exact columns you want.\n",
    "This is almost always expected in AQA exam answers.\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2a. Worked example\n",
    "\n",
    "The query below retrieves only the title and author of every book.\n"
