    "</details>\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "fad75d34",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3c. Practice — filtering members\n",
    "\n",
    "Write a query to show the `FirstName`, `LastName` and `JoinDate` of all members\n",
