  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bcd95ef6",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3e. Practice — NULL values\n",
    "\n",
    "In the `Loan` table, a `NULL` ReturnDate means the book is **still on loan**.\n",
    "The correct SQL to check for NULL is `IS NULL` (not `= NULL`).\n",
    "\n",
    "Write a query to show the `LoanID`, `MemberID` and `LoanDate`\n",
    "of all loans where the book has **not yet been returned**.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "b7b209c7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%sql\n",
    "-- Write your query here\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "6b881064",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<details>\n",
    "<summary>▶ Show answer</summary>\n",
    "\n",
    "```sql\n",
    "SELECT LoanID, MemberID, LoanDate\n",
    "FROM Loan\n",
    "WHERE ReturnDate IS NULL;\n",
    "```\n",
    "</details>\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8480a735",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Part 4 — Sorting Results with ORDER BY\n",
    "\n",
    "`ORDER BY` sorts results by a column.\n",
    "- `ASC` = ascending (A→Z, 0→9) — this is the default\n",
    "- `DESC` = descending (Z→A, 9→0)\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4a. Worked example — alphabetical order\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "dad1d6ef",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%sql\n",
    "SELECT Title, Author\n",
    "FROM Book\n",
    "ORDER BY Title ASC;"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "72116f9b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
