    "### Question 3 [3 marks]\n",
    "\n",
    "The library wants to record a new loan. Member with ID 9 has borrowed\n",
    "the book with ID 10 today (`2024-06-19`). The loan has not yet been returned.\n",
    "\n",
    "Write an SQL statement to add this record to the `Loan` table.\n",
    "The next available `LoanID` is 16.\n"
   ]
